ğŸ“¦ Inventory Management API (FastAPI)

A lightweight Inventory Management System built using FastAPI that allows querying host inventory based on cloud provider, region, status, tags, and IP addresses.

ğŸš€ Features

Load inventory from a JSON file

Fetch all hosts

Search hosts by:

Hostname

Cloud provider (AWS / Azure / GCP)

Region

Active / Inactive status

Tags (key-value)

Private IP

Public IP

Proper error handling using HTTPException

Auto-generated API documentation (Swagger / ReDoc)

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack

Python 3.8+

FastAPI

Uvicorn

JSON-based inventory

